# (feature-image Phase 15 migration note: the generation history, workflow
# pipeline, and thread messages used to live in .feature-image-history.jsonl,
# .feature-image-pipeline.jsonl, and .feature-image-threads.jsonl at the
# repo root. They now live as per-entry JSON files under journal/. The
# journal/ tree is intentionally NOT gitignored — Phase 11 fitness scoring
# and the lineage graph depend on it.)
#
# .editorial-draft-history.jsonl and .editorial-draft-pipeline.jsonl are
# also intentionally tracked. They hold the editorial-review workflow's
# state machine, version history, and annotation log. The editorial-review
# Phase 12 feedback signal (voice-drift aggregation) is computed from them.
# (Candidate for the same journal/-style migration if they start hitting
# merge conflicts — see docs/.../feature-image-generator Phase 15.)
